nodes.text: An Interdictor Star Destroyer took part in the Battle of the Sixela system in 0 ABY. Following the launch of resonance torpedoes toward the system's star, the Interdictor and the rest of the Imperial fleet fled into hyperspace.
This Star Destroyer appears in Alex Wheeler's 2010 book Rebel Force: Uprising, where it was identified only as an Interdictor Star Destroyer.
